cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this skill suite, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "TPS Skill Suite: Autonomous Development Skills for AI Agents"
abstract: >
  A suite of reasoning skills for autonomous AI agents implementing the
  Autonomous Agent Principles framework. Skills include Kata (orchestration),
  Kaizen (incremental improvement), Kaikaku (radical redesign), Hansei
  (reflection), Shiken (novelty probes), and Kiroku (evidence trail management).
  Accompanied by computable metrics (metrics.ps1) and a mechanical integrity
  verifier (verify-suite.ps1). Evaluated across 97+ runs and 5 model families
  (Claude, GPT, Gemini, Grok, Grok Code). Constitutional foundation in the
  companion Autonomous Agent Principles repository.
authors:
